Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage

This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeCoordinationStorage Interface for coordination persistence storage layer.
IAeCounterStore Defines interface for counter store.
IAeLocationVersionSet Defines interface for a set of objects identified by location id and version number.
IAeLocationVersionSet.IEntry Defines the interface for an entry in an IAeLocationVersionSet.
IAePersistedAlarm Represents an alarm that was stored in the persistent store.
IAeProcessStateConnection Defines interface for storing and retrieving process state and variable documents.
IAeProcessStateStorage Defines interface for managing process state and variables in storage.
IAeQueueStorage This interface defines the required methods for a persistent queue store.
IAeScheduleStorageEntry  
IAeStorage Base interface for all storage interfaces.
IAeStorageFactory This interface defines an Active BPEL engine store factory.
IAeStorageProviderFactory Defines methods needed to create storage providers (Database i/o classes).
IAeTransmissionTrackerStorage Interface for the transmission, receive manager storage layer.
IAeURNStorage Defines the methods for storing and retrieving URN mappings.
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractStorage An abstract base class that is extended by all delegating storage impls.
AeAbstractStorageProviderFactory Base class for storage provider factories.
AeCharArrayDocumentReader Delivers an AeFastDocument or standard XML Document as a fixed-length character stream using an in-memory character array.
AeCoordinationStorage A delegating implementation of a coordination storage.
AeCounter Implements persistent counters.
AeDocumentReader Abstract class that delivers an AeFastDocument or standard XML Document as a fixed-length character stream (Java Reader).
AeLocationVersionSet Implements a set of location id + version number pairs.
AeLocationVersionSet.AeLocationVersionEntry Combines a location id and version number for use as a key in a Java Set or Map
AePersistedAlarm A persisted alarm.
AePersistedMessageReceiver This class is used by the SQL version of the QueueStorage to conveniently return AeMessageReceiver objects with a database ID attached.
AePersistentAttachmentManager Implements a persistent attachment manager.
AePersistentQueueManager Implements a persistent queue manager.
AePersistentStoreFactory This persistent store factory provides access to a concrete, singleton implementation of a persistent store factory.
AeProcessStateConnection A delegating implementation of a process state connection.
AeProcessStateStorage A delegating implementation of a process state storage.
AeQueueStorage A delegating implementation of a queue storage.
AeStorageConfig This class is a base for the SQL and Tamino config classes.
AeStorageFactory A basic storage factory - this class creates the various storage objects.
AeStorageUtil Util methods used by the storage layer.
AeTransmissionTrackerStorage A delegating implementation of a transmission/receive storage.
AeURNStorage A delegating implementation of a URN storage.
 

Exception Summary
AeDeadlockException An exception thrown when a database encounters a deadlock.
AeStorageException Standard exception for the storage package.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage Description

This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility.
